the youngest consul

27:40.326 --> 27:42.612
in the history of Rome.

27:43.412 --> 27:46.449
Gaius Octavian...

27:46.582 --> 27:48.368
Caesar.

28:06.185 --> 28:08.176
Esteemed senators...

28:10.147 --> 28:14.265
